TranslationsData.This project was created to automate and:
This project was created to automate and consolidate the necessary information for the game in one place!

Almost all the resources of the application belong to the game CSR2 and are the property of NaturalMotion => Zynga => Take-Two Interactive. The resources are used only to display reference information for the gaming community and nothing more.
